About Game:
************
Can you spot an elephant out of a hundred puzzle pieces? Play Eye Know and show how much you know! We show you an animated and distorted picture and all you have to do is name the image! There are 10 different special animated distortions, and 18 different level packs, including celebrities, animals, logos and landmarks!

Game Features:
**************
-Identify celebrities, animals, and logos
-Click on letters or type your answer
-Use bombs, hints and reveals to help solve levels
-18 level packs, totaling 360 images!
-10 unique animated effects!
